[This file is part of the zabbix-agent-osso package]

Drop-in dir for onboot called scripts that can check a bunch of parameters
early in boot.

Files ending with .sh are executed in lexicographical order. Other files are
ignored.

Environment passed:
- CACHE = path where we can place files to be read by userparameters
- DMESG = path to a file with early dmesg boot info.
